UID:PClKZlFJ8bw7okBhYtk5k
SUMMARY:Guest Stylist Pop-up Event
DTSTAMP:20260325T062329Z
DTSTART:20260325T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description      Nic of Ends of the Earth\, Micki Yeates of Hat
	ch Hair and Company\, and Kitt Spata are teaming up for a queer haircut da
	y Wednesday\, March 25th 11am - 5pm. Haircuts of all lengths are welcome\,
	 but each stylist specializes in slightly different services. If you don't
	 see a service that is appropriate for yourself with one stylist\, please 
	check the others'. This event is meant to be a fun time and designed to br
	ing community together and profits will go towards Kitt&'s travel costs as
	 well as a donation to Utopia Washington. Looking forward to seeing you th
	ere! Sliding scale options are available\, but spots are limited. Please u
	se the special booking link here to secure your appointment: Book Now\n\nh
	ttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/guest-stylist-pop-up-event/18
	234877/2026-03-25T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/guest-stylist-pop-up-even
	t/18234877/2026-03-25T00
