	time\, kids ages 1-3 and their families can enjoy stories\, songs\, and fu
	n learning activities.\n\nLocation Link:\n\nBeacon Hill Branch\n\nRoom Loc
	ation: Meeting Room\n\nRegistration Required: Registration is not required
	.\n\nDetailed Description: Early Learning is a great way fortoddlers and t
	heir families to develop learning\, literacy\, and language skills as well
	 as community with other families.\, We read stories\, sing songs\, and ha
	ve engaging\, educational activities that help kids and their caregivers g
	row together.\n\nEvent Logistics: Registration is not required but these p
	rograms are very popular and the room capacity can fill up quickly.\, Fami
	lies of all ages are welcome\, though this early learning program is inten
	ded for youth aged 1-3\, their caregivers and families.\, Story time lasts
	 for about 30 minutes and it is followed by a playtime for 30 minutes.\, F
	ind out more about\n\nEarly Learning & Story Time\n\nprograms.\n\nContact 
	Us: If you have questions about this event\,\n\nAsk Us\n\nor call 206-386-
	4636.\n\nADA Accommodations: We can provide accommodations for people with
	 disabilities at Library events. Please\n\ncontactLEAP\n\nat least seven d
