	spices for a sauce as you create deeply flavorful dan dan noodles. You’ll 
	also try your hand at methodically rolling and flattening dough with scall
	ions for savory pancakes\, which you’ll pair with a scratch-made dipping s
	auce. By the end of class\, you’ll be ready to recreate the entire menu in
	 your kitchen. \n\nContains pork and dairy. \n\nAbout the instructor: Our 
